data.description: You will not want to miss this charming 3 bedroom & 1.5 bathroom home. This home features two potential living room areas that are both spacious! The kitchen offers ample cabinet space, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and an open view to the dining room. The master suite features a walk-in closet and a half bath. There is a large fenced in back yard. This home has been well maintained, roof and hot water heater are only 4 years old.
